218
00:15:12,879 --> 00:15:13,960
Okay, bye.

219
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:24,720
Huangmei tune?

220
00:15:25,799 --> 00:15:28,159
If it were in a movie...

221
00:15:28,879 --> 00:15:29,919
What?

222
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:31,879
Nothing.

223
00:15:32,279 --> 00:15:34,000
I think I've found the soul.

224
00:15:39,639 --> 00:15:40,840
Could it be?

225
00:15:55,039 --> 00:15:56,039
My husband,

226
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:58,720
